OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny heavy
OL,6,Fshowers, affecting eastern areas soon
OL,7,Ffading during Wednesday evening with
OL,8,Fclear spells developing. Cloud then
OL,9,Fthickens again from the west through
OL,10,Fthe early hours of Thursday, but
OL,11,Flikely staying dry for most. Any
OL,12,Fshowers mainly affecting coastal areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FSome warm, sunny spells
OL,15,Fexpected, but building cloud bringing
OL,16,Fscattered showers, heavy at times.
OL,17,FSome parts probably remaining dry,
OL,18,Fmost likely near coasts by Thursday
OL,19,Fafternoon. Winds becoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
